OL,3,CSouthampton Paddington Bear display
OL,4,Cvandalised
OL,6,FPart of a Paddington Bear display in
OL,7,FSouthampton has been vandalised.
OL,9,FThe bench that the statue of the much
OL,10,Floved character was sitting on in
OL,11,FGuildhall Square was damaged on Sunday.
OL,13,FA nearby cafe took the statue inside
OL,14,Ffor safe-keeping.
OL,16,FStephen Manion Executive Director of
OL,17,FGO! Southampton said: "We were to sad
OL,18,Fhear that on Sunday afternoon,
OL,19,FPaddington's bench had been destroyed
OL,20,Fin Guildhall Square.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
