CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776246948
OL,3,CSouthampton Paddington Bear display
OL,4,Cvandalised
OL,6,F"Luckily, Paddington remains unharmed
OL,7,Fand we are keeping him safe in our
OL,8,Foffice until we can fix the bench
OL,9,Fready for him to return home.
OL,11,F"We will be working on this as quickly
OL,12,Fas possible, so people won't be
OL,13,Fwithout Paddington for long!
OL,15,F"The incident has been reported, and
OL,16,Fwe are working with the Police and
OL,17,Flocal businesses to find out who was
OL,18,Finvolved.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
