OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776246948
OL,3,CSouthampton Paddington Bear display
OL,4,Cvandalised
OL,6,F"Thank you to all the supportive
OL,7,Fcomments online, there is clearly a
OL,8,Flot of love for Paddington in the
OL,9,Fcity."
OL,11,FA Hampshire Police spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"We have received a report of criminal
OL,13,Fdamage to the Paddington bench.
OL,15,F"Our local neighbourhood policing team
OL,16,Fare investigating the matter,
OL,17,Fincluding reviewing CCTV and
OL,18,Fidentifying witnesses."
